Dominate

Active
Psion 10

7 Cooldown

Gain control of an enemy at 2 or less range.
Lasts a number of turns equal one plus (the difference between your Intellect and the target's Will) divided by four.
Minimum 2 turns.

==

Example numbers:
10 Int vs 8 Will: 2 turns
22 Int vs 18 Will: 2 turns
22 Int vs 14 Will: 3 turns
26 Int vs 8 Will: 5 turns

==

Not enough variability in duration?